wikipedia_page.main: Hugo Nevill Money-Coutts, 8th Baron Latymer (1 March 1926 – 10 November 2003) was an English banker and sailor. He inherited the title Baron Latymer from his father, Thomas Burdett Money-Coutts, 7th Baron Latymer.
